title: Sergio Aguero just took a selfie with two of the worlds most powerful men
text:
Sergio Aguero just took a selfie with two of the world's most powerful men 
Breaking News.ie Friday 23rd October, 2015 
David Cameron might have just become blue in more than one way. 
The league leaders were paid a visit by the British prime minister and Chinese president Xi Jinping during the final day of his state visit. 
Previously thought to be a Manchester United fan, Mr Xi was apparently prepared to risk his credibility as a member of the Old Trafford faithful to visit the City academy. 
And it didnâ€™t take long for prolific frontman Sergio Aguero to make the most of the situation....
